{"tid":443092,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IG莫名地disabled...","createTime":"2017-10-21T10:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T11:06:47.000Z","uid":8497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"31670b4c12bc010544f4190a135db763d02edc9c","tid":443092,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"我個ig突然被disabled<br />\n自己登入唔到<br />\n但係其他account仍然search到<br />\n已經過左兩個星期<br />\n每日我都用其他account回報問題<br />\n個ig對我好重要<br />\n我應該無違反過任何守則<br />\n無Warning下就比人disabled<br />\n<br />\n我google過同ig講要話自己被人hack就會有ig回覆<br />\n但好似上面咁講<br />\nig從來無contact番我<br />\n<br />\n我亦都見到有人講如果認識係ig/fb入面既人做可以加快解決<br />\n有無巴絲曾經遇過呢個問題<br />\n又有無巴絲會識係fb ig做既人<br />\n如果真係unlock得番會有薄酬<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eaedfb578c41c261a3b5d4ca2bff5b9138e9dd7","tid":443092,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ece503ff4088b07cbfbaf5eb7cb805b71f7d1d","tid":443092,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有計嗎"},{"pid":"fa08f49f80e332262f4ba0e0b7ae93678023afab","tid":443092,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09431c2b927fb687a00410917d10e1d06623daae","tid":443092,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}